text: Stavangerpark, also known as the city park, is located around Breiavatnet in the centre of Stavanger, Norway. It is a quiet park, with a lot of doves, ducks, swans and other birds. Also in the park is Stavanger Cathedral which dates from around the year 1100. ==External links== * http://www.stavangerpark.com/templates/b3007/images/parkenback2.jpg * http://www.stavangerpark.com/fra_park.jpg * https://web.archive.org/web/20060222200649/http://www.stavangerpark.com/domkirke.jpg- for-web-LARGE.jpg Category:Stavanger Category:Tourist attractions in Stavanger Category:Parks in Norway
